29
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:26,110
Chu Xiuming. Let's clear our debts today!

30
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:31,900
My father, Ba Te'er, died under your sword on the battlefield!

31
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:35,250
Today, I will have you repay with blood!

32
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:39,360
Hu Te! Both sides have come to a truce!

33
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,460
The people are all living peacefully!

34
00:02:41,460 --> 00:02:45,700
This is what your father and the soldiers bought with their fresh blood!

35
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:48,550
Your actions now are inducing warfare!

36
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:49,900
Shut up!

37
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:53,870
You killed my father! Getting revenge for my father is the right thing to do!

38
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:56,110
I did kill Ba Te'er!

39
00:02:56,110 --> 00:03:00,400
Half a year ago, 24 of our soldiers were walking near our border.

40
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:04,350
Your father led 50 soldiers and ambushed our soldiers.

41
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:06,790
He killed more than 10 of our infantrymen.

42
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:08,720
I took 7 men with me and we killed our way out of the tight encirclement.

43
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,090
But your father kept pursuing us!

44
00:03:10,090 --> 00:03:11,870
If I didn't kill him,

45
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:14,420
the soldiers who risked their lives with me would be the ones who died!

46
00:03:14,420 --> 00:03:17,270
Stop arguing! A life for a life!

47
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:20,180
My mother was killed by the Falcon Tribe!

48
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:24,760
My father also killed under your sword while protecting me.

49
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:29,910
Am I supposed to kill all of you to get revenge for my father?

50
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:37,390
Warfare by the border has continued for years.

51
00:03:37,390 --> 00:03:40,060
How many soldiers on both sides have been sacrificed?

52
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:44,550
The cruelty of the battlefield means someone must die!

53
00:03:44,550 --> 00:03:47,860
Our warfare is to protect our country!

54
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:52,680
Every soldier sacrificed, was for our country and for the glory of our ancestors!

55
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:57,130
You're just trying to save your own life!

56
00:03:57,130 --> 00:04:01,530
You destroyed my family! Today, I must take your life!

57
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:03,660
If my life can allow you to put down your hate,

58
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:06,400
can allow you to put down your hate,

59
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:09,130
then take it.

60
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:11,830
Alright! Give me your life!

61
00:04:11,830 --> 00:04:13,330
Don't kill my husband!

62
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:14,970
Stop!

63
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:20,980
