64
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:26,360
Princess! Someone wants to kill my husband! Please uphold justice!

65
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:30,660
Princess! This person killed my father! Please let me kill him!

66
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:33,790
Stop talking. I know what happened between you and the General.

67
00:04:33,790 --> 00:04:36,480
General is my friend, he is not a bad person.

68
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:39,790
Besides, both sides have stopped fighting. Your actions are improper.

69
00:04:39,790 --> 00:04:42,070
Princess!

70
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:45,700
If you insist on doing this, I can only report it to Royal Father.

71
00:04:46,890 --> 00:04:48,930
I do not dare!

72
00:05:02,450 --> 00:05:06,210
The battlefield caused us to lose our family.

73
00:05:06,210 --> 00:05:10,740
But their sacrifice, was not for allowing hatred to continue.

74
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:15,440
It was to allow us to have a better, more peaceful life.

75
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:25,810
Let them go!

76
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:37,020
-Cheers!
-Cheers1

77
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:46,000
Thank you for today, Princess Ma Ya, Prince Consort.

78
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,410
General, just call me Yuan'er.

79
00:05:47,410 --> 00:05:50,750
I'm really not used to that title.

80
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:53,640
You'll get used to it if you hear it a few more times!

81
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:56,630
Come! Prince Consort, have another cup!

82
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:58,220
Here.

83
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:03,370
Your Highness, you seduced Princess Ma Ya without a word!

84
00:06:03,370 --> 00:06:07,190
After we found out you two were together, we were shocked to death!

85
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:12,270
Your Highness, when are you two going to add on more happiness?
<i>(aka pregnancy)</i>

86
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:24,790
