88
00:06:28,810 --> 00:06:33,650
Don't worry! I switched this out for water a long time ago!

89
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,430
Don't tell me your cup is also water!

90
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:39,620
No no no. I won't drink water!

91
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:44,000
That's right. Princess Ma Ya, I have one more request.

92
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,580
Please go ahead.

93
00:06:45,580 --> 00:06:47,390
I'm looking for a medicinal ingredient from the Falcon Tribe.

94
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:50,420
I require the consultation services of a very experienced apothecarist.

95
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:54,490
That's easy enough. I'll take my tribe's apothecarist to come and visit you tomorrow.

96
00:06:54,490 --> 00:06:55,850
Thank you Princess.

97
00:06:55,850 --> 00:06:58,510
She's pregnant! How could you make her run around?

98
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:00,470
Ma Ya, you can just bring anyone. Your body is more important.

99
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:02,750
- Right, right.  
 - Your body is more important.

100
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,700
It's fine!

101
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:08,600
-Congratulations!
-Thank you Princess.

102
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:12,360
-Congratulations, Princess Ma Ya and Prince Consort!
-Thank you!

103
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:24,450
<i>I wonder how Miss Ta Rou is doing?</i>

104
00:07:24,450 --> 00:07:27,200
<i>I still owe her an apology.</i>

105
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:36,490
Miss Ta Rou!

106
00:07:36,490 --> 00:07:39,570
You don't think you should say something to me?

107
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:40,970
I'm sorry!

108
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:43,330
Not that one!

109
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:47,260
