110
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:50,790
Tell me!

111
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:56,400
General and Her Ladyship are very in love. General changed a lot for Her Ladyship.

112
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,940
He is willing to die for her.

113
00:07:57,940 --> 00:08:02,050
But towards you, I do not hold such affection.

114
00:08:02,050 --> 00:08:06,600
If I marry you, I wouldn't be very responsible towards you.

115
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:10,850
You really don't like me at all?

116
00:08:10,850 --> 00:08:13,110
No.

117
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:17,900
Then how can you be sure you won't like me in the future?

118
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:20,390
Please don't force things, Miss Ta Rou.

119
00:08:21,230 --> 00:08:23,050
I don't agree!

120
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:27,570
No matter where you go in the future, I'll go with you!

121
00:08:27,570 --> 00:08:29,990
What will happen to your brother if you leave?

122
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:34,830
Him? He doesn't want me anyway.

123
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:38,830
We've only known each other for a few days.

124
00:08:38,830 --> 00:08:41,210
But you and your brother grew up together.

125
00:08:41,210 --> 00:08:45,790
Why are you willing to trust a stranger like me rather than a family member?

126
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:53,280
Miss Ta Rou. My family died when I was very young.

127
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,830
I am very jealous of those who have family members.

128
00:08:55,830 --> 00:08:59,350
No matter how strict your brother is with you, it's a way of protecting you!

129
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:02,180
