203
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:52,220
Miss Ta Rou disappeared?

204
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:54,460
She came to see yesterday night, asking me to take her away.

205
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:55,970
I refused and she left.

206
00:14:55,970 --> 00:14:59,930
You dare refuse my sister? Come! Let's fight.

207
00:14:59,930 --> 00:15:02,810
Brother Hu Te. It's urgent, we should find miss Ta Rou.

208
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:05,380
Do you where she often goes?

209
00:15:10,090 --> 00:15:12,650
Xiuyuan, quickly go in town to search for her.

210
00:15:12,650 --> 00:15:15,690
Brother Hu Te, send people to look for her.

211
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:20,080
Good. If we can't find Ta Rou, I'm taking you into custody!

212
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:23,400
Did you see Ta Rou?

213
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,360
A girl this tall?

214
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,470
Did you see Ta Rou?

215
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:29,390
