234
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:37,160
Nobody cares about me.

235
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:40,330
I want to leave this place for ever.

236
00:16:40,330 --> 00:16:43,100
Miss Ta Rou, we have a big brother as father.

237
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:45,950
To find you, your brother went to ask us.

238
00:16:45,950 --> 00:16:48,400
How come would he not want you?

239
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:50,730
He always bullies me.

240
00:16:50,730 --> 00:16:52,930
He always hated me.

241
00:16:52,930 --> 00:16:54,450
I... I...

242
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:58,200
Ta Rou.

243
00:16:59,230 --> 00:17:01,150
When I was younger, every time I was angry at you,

244
00:17:01,150 --> 00:17:03,170
you ran to this wall.

245
00:17:03,170 --> 00:17:05,580
I could find you every time.

246
00:17:05,580 --> 00:17:07,450
But as we grew up, I forgot this place.

247
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:09,640
I forgot this place.

248
