That year, 8th Prince Manor suddenly went up in flames.

550
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:16,580
Everyone died inside the  manor.

551
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:24,330
Besides 8th Prince and my aunt's only child, Xiuyuan.

552
00:40:25,850 --> 00:40:29,340
Later, the current emperor took the throne.

553
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:33,910
My father secretly took Xiuyuan to the border and raised him.

554
00:40:34,680 --> 00:40:38,910
And he never told me how it happened.

555
00:40:39,700 --> 00:40:43,320
Then it looks like something was going on behind this!

556
00:40:46,390 --> 00:40:50,160
My Chu family is the 8th Princess Consort's maternal family.

557
00:40:50,700 --> 00:40:55,540
Ever since my parents died, I took care of Xiuyuan by myself.

558
00:40:55,540 --> 00:40:58,160
At the same time, I investigated the 8th Prince's death.

559
00:40:58,160 --> 00:41:00,640
I want to help Xiuyuan restore his identity.

560
