I heard my Royal Father mention it before!

561
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:08,640
Back then, the Crown Prince was wise in politics and sought out men of wisdom and valour who also admonished him.

562
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:10,630
He would certainly be a good emperor!

563
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:14,870
And the Chu family has earned great merit and has been loyal for generations.

564
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:20,070
Jin'er.

565
00:41:21,710 --> 00:41:24,110
This has to do with Xiuyuan's life.

566
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:27,850
I told you this today.

567
00:41:27,850 --> 00:41:29,880
You must guard this secret well.

568
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:37,790
Since I married you, I will do my best for the Chu family.

569
00:41:37,790 --> 00:41:41,500
Starting from today, my heart will be aligned with yours,

570
00:41:41,500 --> 00:41:45,900
